1. cs.RO (Robotics): The paper proposes a method for robot calligraphy using a virtual brush model and trajectory optimization, which falls under the domain of robotics. 
2. cs.GR (Graphics): The paper focuses on generating aesthetically pleasing characters, which is a key aspect of computer graphics. 
3. cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper may involve computer vision techniques for recognizing and analyzing characters. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper may involve AI techniques for optimizing the trajectory of the virtual brush. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper involves control theory and optimization techniques for achieving real-time closed-loop control of the virtual brush.
